<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); width: 135.391px; height: 5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-md5="33145">
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 5px; background-color: rgba(17, 92, 193, 0.99); letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
</section>
<section style="margin: -5px 0px 0px; padding: 20px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: #e8f5fd; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-md5="33145">
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #595959; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 26.25px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-md5="33145">
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; color: #7b7f83; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一是各地区、各有关部门要整合发展财政和社会资金，支持高校学生创新创业活动。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; color: #7b7f83; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">二是高校要优化经费支出结构，多渠道统筹安排资金，支持创新创业教育教学，资助学生创新创业项目。部委属高校按规定使用中央高校基本科研业务费，支持在校学生开展创新科研工作。</span></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; color: #7b7f83; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">三是中国教育发展基金会设立大学生创新创业教育奖励基金。</span></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; color: #7b7f83; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">四是鼓励社会组织、公益团体、企事业单位和个人设立大学生创业风险基金。</span></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; color: #7b7f83; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">五是落实各项扶持政策和服务措施，重点支持大学生到新兴产业创业。</span></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: #7b7f83; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">六是有关部门要加快制定有利于互联网创业的扶持政策。</span></section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><hr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); transform-origin: 0px 0px 0px; transform: scale(1, 0.5); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" />
<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
</section>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (429, '<p><a title="第八届互联网加大赛评审规则" href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/mehSaoy1zrQTgLYhUVCNnQ">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/mehSaoy1zrQTgLYhUVCNnQ</a></p>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (430, '<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="BWVJNVm2">在如今这个移动互联网的时代，想必各位都听说过&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;这个名词，但是不知道有多少同学真的弄懂了&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;的真正意思呢？现阶段&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;虽然被领域所运用，并被很多人提起，但是实际上并没有明确明确&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;与&ldquo;+互联网&rdquo;的区别，事实上两种模式主体不同，当然他适合的产业也就各不相同也不同，不能直接认为&ldquo;+互联网&rdquo;就是&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;，那是错误的。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;与&ldquo;+互联网&rdquo;两者不同</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&ldquo;+互联网&rdquo;更多强势&ldquo;创新&rdquo;。主要是传统行业利用互联网技术和理念，提高为用户服务的效率和质量。&ldquo;+互联网&rdquo;主要是把互联网当做工具使用，只知道怎么用，但是认知一般，应用的都是表面，不深入。类似便利店中使用收款二维码的方式则是&ldquo;+互联网&rdquo;的简单案例。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="BWVJNVm2">&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;更主要强调的是逆向思维。在&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;中互联网会与传统行业形成深度融合，形成全新的发展生态。其会充分发挥互联网在生产要素配置中的优化和集成作用，并将其创新成果融合于经济社会各领域当中，从而提升实体经济的创新力和生产力。&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;比较核心的要义就是依靠互联网平台、信息通信技术实现去中间化，让传统行业焕发全新的生命力。像滴滴打车、CCtalk等网络教育平台就是非常典型的&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;的成功案例，相信一提到这几个案例，各位同学很容易就能够理解到这两者存在的巨大差异了吧。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="BWVJNVm2"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" />了解了&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;到底是什么之后，就到了我们今天要说的真正重点&mdash;&mdash;中国互联网+大学生创新创业大赛。中国大学生互联网+创新创业大赛旨在深化高等教育综合改革，激发大学生的创造力，培养造就&ldquo;大众创业、万众创新&rdquo;的生力军;推动赛事成果转化，促进"互联网+"新业态形成，服务经济提质增效升级;以创新引领创业、创业带动就业，推动高校毕业生更高质量创业就业。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" />迄今为止，中国互联网+创新创业大赛已经成功举办了七届，而第八届也在今年4月正式拉开了帷幕。参赛的团队可以通过登录&ldquo;全国大学生创业服务网&rdquo;（cy.ncss.cn）进行报名。大赛共产生3500个项目入围总决赛（港澳台地区参赛名额单列），其中高教主赛道2000个（国内项目1500个、国际项目500个）、&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;赛道500个、职教赛道500个、萌芽赛道200个、产业命题赛道300个。认识一下互联网+大赛的三大赛道（高教主赛道、职教赛道、红旅赛道）</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="BWVJNVm2">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="BWVJNVm2">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一、互联网+大赛的三大核心赛道<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" />1. 高校主赛道</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" />这个赛道参赛的项目主要以了解和把握&ldquo;四新&rdquo;发展要求，参赛项目不只限于&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;项目，鼓励各类创新创业项目参赛，根据&ldquo;四新&rdquo;建设内涵和产业发展方向选择相应类型分为了以下四组类别：新医科、新工科、新农科、新文科。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">具体赛道为：</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">1）本科生组（创意组、初创组、成长组）</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">2)&nbsp; 研究生组（创意组、初创组、成长组）</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">今年核心注意：教师学校科研成果不得申报创意组，股权的变换需要注意。</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">从名字就可以看得出来，创意组别的参赛项目都具有较好的创意和较为成型的产品原型或者是服务模式，并且没有完成工商登记注册。初创组要求参赛项目工商等各类登记注册未满3年（2019年3月1日及以后注册）。成长组要求的是参赛项目工商等各类登记注册3年以上（2019年3月1日前注册）。减少了融资要求。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2.&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&ldquo;赛道</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" />这个赛道中的项目会对推进革命老区、贫困地区、城乡社区经济社会发展等方面有创新性、实效性和可持续性的作用。目的是将思政教育、专业教育与创新创业教育相结合，传承红色基因，坚定理想信念，全面推进课程思政，涵养青年学生家国情怀；以新工科、新医科、新农科、新文科助力&ldquo;新农村、新农业、新农民、新生态&rdquo;建设，引导师生扎根基层创新创业，推动乡村振兴取得新进展、农业农村现代化迈出新步伐。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 36px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">具体赛道为：</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">1）公益组</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">2）创意组</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">3）创业组</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">今年聚焦&ldquo;新农村、新农业、新农民、新生态&rdquo;建设，围绕乡村&ldquo;产业振兴、人才振兴、文化振兴、生态振兴、组织振兴&rdquo;</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">公益组的参赛项目以社会价值为导向，不以营利为目标，积极弘扬公益精神，在公益服务领域具有较好的创意、产品或服务模式的创业计划和实践。创意组参赛项目基于专业和学科背景或相关资源，解决农业农村和城乡社区发展面临的主要问题，助力乡村振兴和社区治理，推动经济价值和社会价值的共同发展，并且尚未完成工商注册。创业组参赛项目以商业手段解决农业农村和城乡社区发展面临的主要问题、助力乡村振兴和社区治理，实现经济价值和社会价值的共同发展，推动共同富裕，并且注册了公司。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3.职教赛道</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这个赛道以高职中职部分职教本科为主，以推进职业教育领域创新创业教育改革，组织学生开展就业型创业实践为核心。设计创新类：以技术、工艺或商业模式创新为核心优势；商业类：以商业运营潜力或实效为核心优势；工匠类：以体现敬业、精益、专注、创新为内涵的工匠精神为核心优势作为导向。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">具体赛道为：</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">1）创业组</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">2）创意组</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">今年核心注意：教师学</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">校科研成果不得申报创意组，</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不得借用他人项目参赛，</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">股权的变换需要注意。</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">参赛项目在大赛通知下发之日前已完成工商等各类登记注册，且公司注册年限不超过5年（2017年3月1日及以后注册）。参赛项目具有较好的创意和较为成型的产品原型、服务模式或针对生产加工工艺进行创新的改良技术，在大赛通知下发之日前尚未完成工商等各类登记注册</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">二、互联网+大赛的三大核心价值</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" />价值观是驱动人生奋斗的核心引力。为何要参加互联网+大赛，大赛对于大学生的价值在哪里？我们可以从三个层面看到：</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1.促进人才成长教育（专创融合教育、思政教育、五育并举）深层次培育</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" />互联网+大赛绝对是一个展现同学们心中真正热爱和梦想的好平台，因为在参赛的整个过程中，存在着更高更广阔更新的视野和通道，加速同学们认知世界，改变世界的机会。学会尝试真实迎接复杂的社会责任与挑战，积极的利用专业所学人生所能融合去创造新产品、模式、技术，促进人生、社会、国家的更高层次繁荣与文明。全流程模拟了一个创意产品的完整生命流程，其中包括创意的产生、可行性的分析、市场需求的模拟分析、产品的研发设计再到产品的最终完善和推广销售，可以说是无所不包无所不含。升华精神高度，点燃远大理想、培育家国情怀，锻炼奋斗精神，孕育崇高品德，践行社会主义接班人的使命。真正推动教育创新，促进人才成长教育深层次培育。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2.完善能力锻炼，促进职业成长</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">大赛对于学生们优秀能力体系的锤炼是同等条件下不可比拟的，这些能力单单在学校中是非常难以得到训练提升的，一个人优秀高端能力的强弱决定了他职业发展可能发展到达的境界。大学时间有限而成长无限。大赛对于从基础的表达，文案排版能力、路演能力到执行能力和领导能力等都是高效训练。只有历经思考与行动才能产生对应能力增长，而大赛将会对这些能力得到短时间急速增长。当然，项目获得融资渠道和资源将会扩展，就业与创业的渠道也会扩大，促进职业机会扩大。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">.促进</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">更高层级的教学相长与教师业务水平提升，专业人培升级</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">2018年印发的《教育部关于加快建设高水平本科教育全面提高人才培养能力的意见》要求深化创新创业课程体系、教学方法、实践训练、队伍建设等关键领域改革。加强创新创业示范高校建设，强化创新创业导师培训，发挥&lsquo;互联网+&rsquo;大赛引领推动作用，提升创新创业教育水平&rdquo;。这就对教师的能力提升提出了挑战，&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;大赛是创新创业教育的手段而非目的，是创新创业教学成果的集中检验和高校科技成果向全社会集中展示的平台，拓展了高校创新创业教育工作的思路。我们需要重构对标顶层设计、竞赛管理、师资建设，构建双创教育全新战略定位，搭建实践平台，去真正提高双创师资综合能力，全面提升学校创新创业教育质量与人才培育的提升。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">三、互</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">联网+大赛的三大获奖核心法宝</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">最后，我们怎样去打造出一个属于我们自己的优秀项目？张老师给3大核心法宝，对标评审规则，从项目出发看自己。</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1.体现教育渠道与个人能力成长</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">大赛其中之一的目的在以赛促学，以赛促创，培养创新创业生力军。激发学生的创造力，聚焦&ldquo;五育&rdquo;融合创新创业教育实践，激发青年学生创新创造热情，激励广大青年扎根中国大地了解国情民情，锤炼意志品质， 开拓国际视野，在创新创业中增长智慧才干，把激昂的青春梦融入伟大的中国梦，努力成长为德才兼备五育并举的的有为人才与新时代社会主义合格建设者。大赛需要展示出<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">真正助推学生，真实驱动，教育创新，实践创业，给与学生真正意义上的能力锤炼成长与教育价值导向，对<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&rdquo;</span>四新学科&ldquo;、&rdquo;职业教育&ldquo;人才培育的点，学校的支持表现。包括</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">项目充分体现团队解决复杂问题的综合能力和高级思维，这就是大赛的意义。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2.展示优秀队伍、具备商业前景与创新性</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea">创新是永恒的话题，只有富有创新性的产品才能够吸引到审评员的目光，也可以说是一个优秀产品的灵魂所在。第五届大赛的季军项目：智网云联&mdash;&mdash;无限共算全球算力交易平台就是一个非常好的例子。其借助P2P网络连接遍布全球的终端设备成功实现了低廉价格的计算力，成功解决了当前共算平台的痛点问题&mdash;&mdash;价格，同时这个问题也是用户的最大需求，比较哪个用户不想使用到便宜又好用的产品呢？显然，这才是一个非常成功的创新案例，记住，在创新的同时一定要切入市场痛点。商业性和团队性在大赛中同样有着举足轻重的作用，项目需要突出有可行性预测的盈利，一般会表现在项目的市场前景和规模两方面。而团队性则代表着你的团队是否是一个值得投资人信赖的关键要素，体现团队对创新创业所需知识（专业知识、商业知识、行业知识等）与技能（计划、组织、领导、控制、创新等）的娴熟掌握与应用，展现创新创业教育提升创业者综合能力的效力。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">团队的组成、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">能力结构、经历背景、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">团队与项目关系的真实性都是重要点展现点。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3.表达社会价值意义<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">大赛有方向的追求带动社会发展进步，我们的创业项目直接提供就业岗位的数量和质量以及</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">项目间接带动就业的能力和规模。都是在汇报材料需要展示出来的。其次，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">项</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">目对社会文明、生态文明、民生福祉等方面的积极推动作用，表达当代青年的作为也是特别好展示的点，整个评分点也是环环相扣。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" data-pid="HpSqNJea"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /><br /></p>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (431, '<section style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.6rem; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">4月9日，第十三届蓝桥杯全国软件和信息技术专业人才大赛（软件类）省赛成功举办。软件工程学院派出120名同学（Web应用开发组38人，算法组82人）参加此次大赛。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">4月28日，比赛成绩揭晓，全校共有103人蓝桥杯获奖，突破历史,其中软件学院就有62人获奖。全校共7名同学取得省赛一等奖，其中软件工程学院5名。（PS：取得省赛一等奖就意味着获得了参加国赛的入场券哦）</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">此次比赛有两个&ldquo;最&rdquo;值得我们关注：</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">一、Web组/算法组获奖人数全校占比最多：</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">据悉，此次蓝桥杯比赛新增Web应用开发组赛道，Web组全校共有33名同学获奖，其中软件学院27人：1人获一等奖，10人获二等奖，16人获三等奖。其中Web组的一等奖、二等奖全部是软件学院取得！</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">算法组全校共70名同学获奖，其中软件学院35人。全校6人获得一等奖，软件学院占4人；全校23人获二等奖，软件学院占15人。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">二、Web组获奖人数全省占比最多：</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">Web组比赛全省共有23个高校共137人获奖，23个高校中不乏南昌大学、江西师范大学、南昌航空大学、江西财经大学、江西农业大学等全省前列的大学，但是我校学子顶住压力，软件工程学院学子更是突出重围，共27人在比赛中获奖，获奖人数位居全省高校第一！！！</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">此次大赛2021级的同学表现非常出色，专科班的同学表现不俗，其中软件技术（UI方向）的C200107班曾勇同学参加本科组的比赛拿到了一等奖，成功晋级国赛！</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">每一个奖项都来之不易</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">每一份付出都必有收获</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">蓝桥杯大赛是由教育部就业指导中心支持，工业和信息化部人才交流中心举办的获得行业深度认可的IT类科技竞赛，是高校教育教学改革和创新人才培养的重要竞赛项目，是教育部认可的57项全国大学生学科竞赛顶级赛事。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">学校和学院对此次大赛非常重视，很早就未雨绸缪，规划布局，在我院联系校领导范红铭校长与学院温洪波院长的大力支持下，副院长柴亚辉博士、李俊带领学院师生尽早进行大赛的各项准备工作，鲍庆军书记和学工辅导员们宣传动员，鼓励同学们积极参加比赛。李卫勇、付腾达老师为负责人的指导教师团队更是紧锣密鼓的开启线上、线下培训，临近比赛时多次举行与正赛环境一样的线上模拟赛。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">此次大赛取得的优异成绩充分展示了我院学子较高的专业技能和良好的精神风貌，未来我院将继续积极参加各级各类技能竞赛以检验教学效果，真正达到以赛促学、以赛促教、以赛促练的目的，从而带动教育教学质量全面提升。</span></p>
</section>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<section style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.6rem;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">获奖名单</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><img class="am-img-responsive am-img-thumbnail am-u-sm-10 am-u-sm-centered" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #dddddd; width: 510.562px; padding: 2px; float: none; position: relative; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; line-height: 1.6; border-radius: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="喜报！蓝桥杯大赛我院大爆发，取得历史性大突破，Web组获奖全省第一！" src="http://rjxy.jxuspt.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20220501/1651388481161903.png" alt="喜报！蓝桥杯大赛我院大爆发，取得历史性大突破，Web组获奖全省第一！" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><img class="am-img-responsive am-img-thumbnail am-u-sm-10 am-u-sm-centered" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #dddddd; width: 510.562px; padding: 2px; float: none; position: relative; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; line-height: 1.6; border-radius: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="喜报！蓝桥杯大赛我院大爆发，取得历史性大突破，Web组获奖全省第一！" src="http://rjxy.jxuspt.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20220501/1651388501215561.png" alt="喜报！蓝桥杯大赛我院大爆发，取得历史性大突破，Web组获奖全省第一！" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><img class="am-img-responsive am-img-thumbnail am-u-sm-10 am-u-sm-centered" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #dddddd; width: 510.562px; padding: 2px; float: none; position: relative; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; line-height: 1.6; border-radius: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="喜报！蓝桥杯大赛我院大爆发，取得历史性大突破，Web组获奖全省第一！" src="http://rjxy.jxuspt.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20220501/1651388520678959.png" alt="喜报！蓝桥杯大赛我院大爆发，取得历史性大突破，Web组获奖全省第一！" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px;">&nbsp;</p>
<section style="box-sizing: border-box;">
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.6rem; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;">少年不惧岁月长，彼方尚有荣光在！热烈祝贺获奖同学取得的优异成绩并预祝进入国赛的五位同学能在国赛中再创佳绩，同时希望此次比赛没有获奖的同学汲取经验，不要气馁！</span></p>
</section>
</section>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (432, '<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 48px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">一、&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">文档目的</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 19px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">为产品的使用者（学生）熟悉产品的各个功能点和日常使用提供参考。</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 48px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">二、&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">产品主要页面详细说明</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">1、<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">大赛首页</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">首屏：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147241940942.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147241940942.png" alt="图1.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">顶部栏：包括首页、投融资、创业孵化、筑梦之旅、International Participant Application for Higher Education Track，点击分别对应进入相应板块或活动页面。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">投融资板块分为寻找融资、寻找项目两个栏目，为创业项目和投资人提供对接通道；创业孵化板块提供热点创业园区介绍、园区活动实时推介等内容；筑梦之旅为第七届大赛同期举办的&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;活动，欢迎进行关注并报名参与。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">右上角为登录及注册入口。点击&ldquo;登录&rdquo;，跳转登录页面，点击&ldquo;注册&rdquo;进入注册页面。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">大创网新用户登录后需接受《全国大学生创业服务网服务条款》，方可继续进行报名参赛、报名&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;活动等其他操作（未通过学籍校验不能报名参赛或参加&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;活动）。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">大赛页面第一屏主要展示了大赛的主办单位、主题等基本信息，并为大赛各页面提供了入口。大赛报名启动后，点击&ldquo;报名参赛&rdquo;按钮将跳转至相应报名参赛页（此处判断用户是否登录，如果没有登录则会先跳转到登录页面进行登录；如果是已登录用户判断用户是否已完善个人信息，如果未完善个人信息则会进入身份选择页面，请选择&ldquo;创业者&rdquo;身份后，进一步完善个人信息；如已完善个人信息则会跳转至个人中心页）。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">首屏右上角六边形的图形为大赛官方微信公众号，鼠标放置该处时，将弹出大创网官方微信平台二维码及大赛官方微信号二维码，可扫描进行关注，掌握大赛动态或咨询报名事宜。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">第二屏：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147324958153.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147324958153.png" alt="图2.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">第二屏为大赛动态、省市高校动态，这里将及时发布关于大赛的重要通知、新闻、活动以及各省市、高校大赛组织的动态新闻等，点击&ldquo;更多&rdquo;之后进入大赛动态、省市高校动态详情页。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147362504232.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147362504232.png" alt="图3.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">该页为大赛动态、省市高校动态的列表页，顶部是动态搜索栏，大赛动态和省市高校动态可在该列表进行切换，右侧为与大赛相关的推荐阅读，点击列表中的文章后进入该文的详情页。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">第三屏：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147440943198.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147440943198.png" alt="图4.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">第三屏为大赛的重要信息页，包括大赛进程时间安排、奖项设置、参赛组别、参赛类别、大赛组委会联系方式<strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: red;">（赛事问题请通过大赛官方微信公众号进行咨询）</span></strong>以及大赛相关文档资料的下载等，并且提供常见问题解答的链接及大赛各省市联系方式<strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: red;">（报名参赛前请仔细阅读常见问题。全国总决赛阶段前，参赛团队如有赛事相关问题，请咨询所在院校大赛负责人或点击各省联系方式，电话咨询所在省市）。</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">第四屏：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147484370991.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147484370991.png" alt="图5.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">第四屏为大赛的官方宣传视频，在该板块将实时更新大赛最新的宣传视频。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">第五屏：</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147511425452.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147511425452.png" alt="图6.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">第五屏为往期大赛精彩回顾页面，展示上一届大赛获奖项目，宣传视频等资料。该页底部留有官网和大赛的微信公众号。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">、寻找项目-项目列表、搜索页</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147552791457.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147552791457.png" alt="图7.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">该页展示在本站创建项目并通过审核的创业项目，设置有搜索框、选择筛选项两种方式进行筛选需要查找的项目。筛选项包括以下内容：所属领域、学校科技成果转化情况、融资阶段、所在地区（地区为省份级别）。点击项目列表中某个项目则跳转进入查看项目详情（注册成为创业者或专家方可查看）。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">3</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">、项目详情页</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147601863095.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147601863095.png" alt="图8.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">项目详情页根据不同的用户身份角色查看的内容有所不同，角色分别设置有：创业者、专家。不同角色将浏览到不同内容的项目信息。创业者仅可查看到项目基本信息（项目概述、项目进展、融资阶段）；针对专家，若您的项目隐私设置为保密，则专家仅可查看到项目基本信息（项目概述、项目进展、融资阶段），若您的项目隐私设置为公开，则专家可查看到项目概述、项目进展、团队成员（基本信息）、融资情况、专利情况、工商注册等部分信息。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 48px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">一、&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">登录注册、<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: black;">成为创业者</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">1、<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">登录页面，填写账号（注册账号使用的手机号、身份证号、邮箱）、密码、验证码进行登录。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147626690668.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147626690668.png" alt="图9.png" /></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">若忘记密码，则点击&ldquo;找回密码&rdquo;跳转到找回密码页面，若未注册则点击&ldquo;注册&rdquo;按钮跳转到用户注册页面。</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">、用户注册页面</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">填写相应信息，进行注册。注册成功后点击&ldquo;立即登录&rdquo;返回登录页面，登录后弹出以下页面：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147728116076.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147728116076.png" alt="10.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">注册成功后可进行身份选择：创业者（点击&ldquo;立即创建项目&rdquo;，参赛或融资请选择该身份）或专家（点击&ldquo;立即认证专家&rdquo;）。<strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: red;">请参赛者务必点击&ldquo;立即创建项目&rdquo;成为创业者，勿选择&ldquo;立即认证专家&rdquo;。请注意：身份选择前请再次确认所选身份，身份选择后将无法进行身份转换。</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">四、学生-个人中心相关页面</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">1.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">立即创建项目（学生）-完善个人信息</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147760324780.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147760324780.png" alt="11.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">选择&ldquo;创业者&rdquo;身份，点击&ldquo;立即创建项目&rdquo;后，需完善个人信息并进行学籍学历信息验证（提交申请后，个人中心显示&ldquo;学籍校验未通过&rdquo;则无法进行报名参赛、报名&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;活动等其他操作）。填写的相关信息如上所示，包括：个人头像、电子邮箱、学历层次、所在院校、入学时间及毕业时间、专业名称。<strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: red;">若无法搜索到您所在院校，请联系所在院校负责大赛的老师，由所在院校联系省级负责人，并由省级负责人统一联系大赛组委会，由大赛组委会统一处理。</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147778145359.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147778145359.png" alt="12.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">个人信息填写成功后，可点击&ldquo;创建项目&rdquo;，进行项目的创建、报名参赛等操作，也可选择暂不创建，返回个人中心。</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">2.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">学生的个人中心</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">我创建的项目</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147831568432.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147831568432.png" alt="13.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋;">用户可以在&ldquo;我创建的项目&rdquo;里查看已经创建的创业项目（点击&ldquo;报名参赛&rdquo;，填写参赛信息并确认提交，完成报名参赛），如果未创建项目则可点击&ldquo;创建项目&rdquo;进行创建。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 32.7273px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 32.7273px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">请注意：1.一个创业者账号可创建三个项目，但仅允许一个项目报名参赛（所创建项目名称不可与库内其他项目名称重复），且创建者需为项目团队负责人。在报名系统未关闭期间可自由编辑、修改项目相关信息。2.项目一旦创建完成将无法修改项目名称，如果需更改项目名称，要删除项目重新创建。（如果项目已通过审核进入校赛或者省赛，删除后项目会退回到待审核状态，请谨慎操作。删除项目前须及时和学校或者省里联系，以便在删除项目后，重新申报的项目可以再次进行审核，以免影响项目参赛）。</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">查看项目详情：</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">个人中心点击项目名称，可以查看项目参赛信息、项目基本信息、团队信息、融资情况、工商信息、专利情况等信息。</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">新建项目</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">第一步：填写项目必填信息</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147855700702.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147855700702.png" alt="14.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147885254586.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147885254586.png" alt="15.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">请注意：若已注册公司，当填写法人身份及股东身份时，在校及毕业5年内的毕业生请选择&ldquo;学生&rdquo;身份。并确保所填信息真实有效。</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">第二步：填写项目其他信息</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147915601865.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147915601865.png" alt="16.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">完成第一步填写项目必填信息后进入第二步，添加项目的团队成员（按照<strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;">所在院校的所属国家和地区</strong>划分归属中国大陆、港澳台或国际团队成员，中国大陆及港澳台地区的团队成员通过邀请方式添加，详见P19页；对于国际团队成员需填写其详细信息进行添加，详见P21页；对于报名高教主赛道师生共创组的项目允许添加教师类团队成员，详见P23页）、指导教师、已获专利信息。如不填写直接点击&ldquo;完成创建&rdquo;即可创建成功创业项目。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">请注意：1.如需报名参加大赛，成功邀请的团队成员至少为3人，原则上不多于15人（含团队负责人），须为项目的实际核心成员。2.仅允许报名高教主赛道师生共创组的项目添加教师类的团队成员，成功邀请的团队成员至少为3人（含团队负责人、学生类团队成员，不含教师类团队成员），原则上不多于15人（含团队负责人、学生类团队成员、教师类团队成员）。</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<h2 style="margin: 16px auto 0px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; line-height: 70px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">邀请中国大陆及中国港澳台地区团队成员具体流程</span></h2>
<h4 style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal;">第一步：完成注册及学籍校验操作。中国大陆及中国港澳台地区的团队成员需首先在全国大学生创业服务网（<a style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; text-decoration-line: none;" href="https://cy.ncss.cn/" target="https://cy.ncss.cn/talentproject/_blank"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: windowtext;">https://cy.ncss.cn</span></a>）上进行注册（其账号与学信账号通用），并验证个人学籍信息。</span></h4>
<h4 style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal;">第二步：邀请团队成员。团队负责人登录全国大学生创业服务网，在添加团队成员版块搜索团队成员&ldquo;姓名+手机号&rdquo;进行添加（</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal;">被邀请的团队成员须为注册用户且完成以下步骤：登录大创网-选择创业者身份-完善个人信息-通过学籍校验。）</span></h4>
<h4 style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red; font-weight: normal;">注意：务必请团队负责人搜索并添加团队成员。</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal;">。</span></h4>
<h4 style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal;">第三步：团队成员完成&ldquo;确认邀请&rdquo;操作。团队负责人邀请团队成员后，需要相应的团队成员关注&ldquo;全国大学生创业服务网&rdquo;微信公众号，点击菜单栏进入&ldquo;我的消息&rdquo;页完成确认操作，方可邀请成功。流程如下：</span></h4>
<ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-type: none; border-bottom: 1px dashed #dddddd; background: url('../../../web/images/arrow_3.jpg') 5px 16px no-repeat;">
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">1.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">关注公众号：关注&ldquo;全国大学生创业服务网&rdquo;微信公众号。</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619147962253208.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619147962253208.png" alt="17.png" /></p>
<ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-type: none; border-bottom: 1px dashed #dddddd; background: url('../../../web/images/arrow_3.jpg') 5px 16px no-repeat;">
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">2.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">微信绑定：进入微信公众号后，输入关键词&ldquo;微信登录&rdquo;，公众号将自动回复登录入口，完成学信网账号与微信账号绑定流程并保持登录状态。</span></p>
</li>
<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-type: none; border-bottom: 1px dashed #dddddd; background: url('../../../web/images/arrow_3.jpg') 5px 16px no-repeat;">
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">3.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">完成&ldquo;确认邀请&rdquo;：退出上述&ldquo;微信绑定&rdquo;页面，重新进入&ldquo;全国大学生创业服务网&rdquo;公众号，点击菜单栏进入&ldquo;我的消息&rdquo;页完成确认邀请操作。</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; font-weight: normal;">第四步：团队负责人查看邀请回复，团队负责人关注&ldquo;全国大学生创业服务网&rdquo;微信公众号，点击菜单栏进入&ldquo;我的消息&rdquo;页，可查看团队成员邀请回复（接受/拒绝）。具体流程如下：</span></h4>
<p style="margin: auto auto 16px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 19px; line-height: 30px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">1.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">关注公众号：步骤同上。</span></p>
<p style="margin: auto auto 16px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 19px; line-height: 30px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">2.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">微信绑定：步骤同上。</span></p>
<p style="margin: auto auto 16px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 19px; line-height: 30px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">3.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">查看邀请回复：点击菜单栏进入&ldquo;我的消息&rdquo;页进行查看。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">添加国际团队成员</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: auto auto 16px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 30px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">请按照国际团队成员所在院校的所属国家添加相应信息，包括姓名（英文填写）、国籍、高校、高校所在国家、专业、学历层次、入学时间、毕业时间、手机号、电子邮箱。</span></p>
<p style="margin: auto auto 16px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 30px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">请注意：</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">1.</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">国际团队成员姓名使用英文填写，其余信息请均使用中文填写。2.若添加的国际团队成员为中国学籍学历，请按照添加&ldquo;中国大陆及中国港澳台团队成员&rdquo;流程进行添加。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148001574356.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148001574356.png" alt="18.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">添加教师类团队成员</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">仅报名高教主赛道师生共创组的项目允许添加教师类团队成员，且编辑项目信息时&ldquo;师生共创&rdquo;一项须选择&ldquo;是&rdquo;才可添加，填写信息包括：真实姓名、国籍（默认中国）、院校所在国家（默认中国）、所在院校、所在部门、职称、手机号码、电子邮箱。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">请注意：真实姓名、国籍、院校所在国籍可填写英文，其余信息均填写中文。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148019352078.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148019352078.png" alt="19.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">我参与的项目</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148050870736.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148050870736.png" alt="20.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">中国大陆及中国港澳台地区的团队成员用户可以在&ldquo;我参与的项目&rdquo;里查看自己参与的创业项目，但不可以进行报名参赛/取消报名等其它操作。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">报名红旅活动</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148519590306.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148519590306.png" alt="21.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148530967335.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148530967335.png" alt="image.png" /><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148544722103.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148544722103.png" alt="image.png" /><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148548296308.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148548296308.png" alt="image.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">通过首页导航键&ldquo;筑梦之旅&rdquo;进入报名页面或进入个人中心点击&ldquo;参加青年红色筑梦之旅活动&rdquo;报名红旅活动，并点击&ldquo;立即报名&rdquo;报名红旅活动。勾选相应项目，点击确定后即完成&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;报名。活动详情请关注所在省市、院校的具体安排。若需取消报名参加&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;活动，如下图，再次点击&ldquo;参加青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;活动，<strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;">勾除</strong>该项并点击确定后即可取消报名。<strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: red;">在全国大学生创业服务网上创建的项目，均可报名参加&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;活动。</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148596488275.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148596488275.png" alt="image.png" /><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148600162727.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148600162727.png" alt="image.png" /><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148605813928.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148605813928.png" alt="image.png" /></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 28px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings; color: red;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">报名参赛</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">完成项目的创建后即可报名参赛，需选择参赛赛道、参赛组别及参赛类别，如下图，选择完成后点击&ldquo;确认参赛&rdquo;即可进入参赛的审核环节（项目报名完成后，由团队负责人所在院校进行审核）。<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: red;">请注意：1.填写报名参赛信息后，如该项目不符合所报赛道及组别的相应要求，则无法提交参赛，系统会对项目不符合要求的信息进行提示。请按照参赛要求重新填写或更换其他赛道、组别。2.选择&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;赛道的项目需已报名参加&ldquo;青年红色筑梦之旅&rdquo;活动。</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148648463808.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148648463808.png" alt="24.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">请注意：报名参赛后团队负责人如进行账号的注销、变更操作，项目信息将自动删除，如要进行账号注销和变更请在报名参赛前进行操作。</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148660903189.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148660903189.png" alt="25.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">请仔细阅读各赛道参赛条件后再进行报名，若您填写的项目信息不符合所报赛道及组别的参赛要求，您将无法报名。</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148690413184.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148690413184.png" alt="26.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 33px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">报名成功后，项目即进入&ldquo;等待学校审核&rdquo;状态，如有疑问，请联系学校跟进审核情况，避免影响参赛。可在个人中心&ldquo;本届大赛参赛项目进度&rdquo;处查看项目状态（见下图）。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148709532931.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148709532931.png" alt="27.png" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 33px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">报名参赛后，如需更改项目的参赛信息（参赛赛道、参赛组别、参赛类别），</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">请进入个人中心的&ldquo;我创建的项目&rdquo;中点击该项目标签中的&ldquo;取消报名&rdquo;（如上图）后，重新报名参赛。<strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: red;">请注意，已报名参赛项目可能已经通过校级、省级审核，所以请在&ldquo;取消报名&rdquo;前，联系所在院校及省市，以免影响项目参赛。</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 33px;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">关注（待上线）</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: right;"><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">我的消息</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">查看各类通知消息。团队负责人可能收到如下信息：团队成员回复邀请的提醒信息；团队成员可能收到如下信息：团队负责人邀请团队成员加入的提醒信息、团队负责人删除团队成员的提醒信息。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0px auto 0px 52px; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: Wingdings;">l<span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">个人设置</span></strong></p>
<h3 style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 34px;"><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋;">个人中心的&ldquo;设置&rdquo;板块可修改个人头像、密码。其他个人信息修改时需同时通过学籍学历验证方可修改。一旦项目报名参赛，个人信息不可修改，如需修改请点击&ldquo;取消报名&rdquo;操作或删除项目。</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">注意：</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red; font-weight: normal;">完善个人信息时若未通过学籍学历校验（个人中心左上角出现红底白字&ldquo;学籍校验不通过&rdquo;字样），</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red;">请点击&ldquo;校验必看&rdquo;查看学籍校验不通过处理办法</span><span style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋; color: red; font-weight: normal;">，然后点击&ldquo;设置&rdquo;，重新填写学籍学历信息提交校验（填写信息需与学信档案信息保持一致方可通过验证）。</span></h3>
<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; color: #101010; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><img style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" title="1619148738692921.png" src="http://www.gdhvc.edu.cn/uploads/allimg/210423/1619148738692921.png" alt="28.png" /></p>');
