<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;"><img class="am-img-responsive am-img-thumbnail am-u-sm-10 am-u-sm-centered" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #dddddd; width: 510.562px; padding: 2px; float: none; position: relative; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; line-height: 1.6; border-radius: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="软件工程学院大学生创新创业大赛答辩现场剧透来袭" src="http://rjxy.jxuspt.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20220612/1654992319120229.jpg" alt="软件工程学院大学生创新创业大赛答辩现场剧透来袭" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 14px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 14px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">随后，评委老师根据不同参赛类别的作品一依次进行了有针对性的提问，就项目的继续完善提出了指导性意见，给没有经验的选手引导鼓励。最后倪锋院长对这些项目进行点评并给予鼓励做出下一步指示。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;"><img class="am-img-responsive am-img-thumbnail am-u-sm-10 am-u-sm-centered" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #dddddd; width: 510.562px; padding: 2px; float: none; position: relative; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; line-height: 1.6; border-radius: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" title="软件工程学院大学生创新创业大赛答辩现场剧透来袭" src="http://rjxy.jxuspt.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20220612/1654992361205155.jpg" alt="软件工程学院大学生创新创业大赛答辩现场剧透来袭" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 14px;">创新创业学院院长：倪锋院长</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 14px;">&ldquo;任何一个成熟的项目，都是源于一个奇思妙想，一点点微光一般的想法。&rdquo;让大学校园创新意识、创业能力的教育与培训工作得到进一步的发展，更为大学生在走出校门前提供了一个创业实践的平台、一条争取风险投资的途径，此次大赛迸发出的激情与朝气将促使其成为学生素质教育的新载体。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (488, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为培养大学生敢闯会创的可贵素质，为江软学生绽放自我、展现风采、服务国家提供舞台，</span>6月19日，江西软件职业技术大学2022年&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;大学生创新创业校级决赛在路演大厅成功举行。本次大赛以&ldquo;互联网+&rdquo;成就梦想　创新创业开辟未来为主题，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">今年</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月份至今，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">江西软件职业技术大学</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">全面部署大赛组织工作，各二级学院积极响应，</span>&ldquo;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">江软</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;">&rdquo;学子踊跃参加。历时</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个月，经过组织动员、培训讲座、项目辅导、二级学院初赛、校级决赛等阶段，共吸引了</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">3242</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个项目参赛，</span>5000余名师生参与，覆盖学校所有二级学院，申报数量、参与人数创学校历史之最。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A18%3A38%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=1971159518&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=L9vx8OYqKSX48mW2Lef5HSozNQM%3D" width="696" height="421" /></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">经由</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">院级</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">初赛、复赛评审选拔后，最终</span>27个项目晋级校</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">级</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">决赛，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">比赛分项目展示和评审答辩两个环节</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参赛团队创意层出，应答自如</span>,充分展现了江软学子&ldquo;敢闯会创&rdquo;的良好风貌。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A19%3A14%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=1971159555&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=6DpP01YvBPDLdGpDgeRDQPgMf84%3D" width="705" height="402" /></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 10.5pt; text-indent: 21pt;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 10.5pt; text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">江西软件职业技术大学</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">聘请由省内知名的企业家、投资人和双创导师组成的评委团对参赛项目逐一路演、点评、打分，为项目后续发展建言献策，帮助项目打磨优化。经过</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一天的</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">激烈角逐，最终</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个项目脱颖而出。它们分别是</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">：</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 10.5pt; text-indent: 21pt; text-align: center;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A46%3A18%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20220621164555.png?Expires=1971161178&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=oOgt%2FxYVBlOf%2BGrpv4KUk3G0rZk%3D" /></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; background: #ffff00;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">优秀项目风采展示</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; background: #ffff00;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">：</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; background: #ffff00;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A23%3A02%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=1971159782&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=%2BHDRjckvy3YezIWX%2F68WB05rzeI%3D" width="707" height="404" /></span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 42pt;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（项目组：《区块赋能，司法链动》）</span></span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt;">&laquo;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&ldquo;我们的创意来源于江西法学会的一个专业课题，为此构建了一个政法区块链平台并收到了江西省委的感谢信，他们将我们所做的东西投入使用，我们团队认为这是一个很好的契机，于是进行深入搭建与创意打造。&rdquo;</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt; text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;--项目负责人：<strong>柯子梦</strong></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A31%3A15%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.png?Expires=1971160275&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=Ls7KQu37wFhl7gtS1lfnW57AvRs%3D" width="708" height="405" /></span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 42pt;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（项目组：《防疫先锋</span>&mdash;&mdash;中小学校园防疫&mdash;站式解决方案》）</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt;">&laquo;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&ldquo;我们的项目理念是&ldquo;科技防疫，助力常态化抗疫&rdquo;。在决定做这个项目以来，创新创业课程不仅带给了我们许多的创新创业知识，促使我们思考如何应用专业去解决实际问题，还培养了我们的动手能力，将理论与实践相结合帮助更快的了解市场。&rdquo;</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt; text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;--</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">项目负责人：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">廖辰宇</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A34%3A17%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.png?Expires=1971160457&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=tIkXDfijkg%2B3gN62gwHB0qVKDug%3D" width="710" height="404" /></span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 73.5pt; text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; （项目组：《</span>&ldquo;追寻红色记忆&rdquo;基于VR技术的交互式党史文化传承馆》）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt;">&laquo;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&ldquo;我们的项目优势就在于采用了一些市面上暂时未有的技术，对引擎进行二次开发，成本低，应用范围广，并结合我们的专业知识，能更好地帮助项目的落地孵化。&rdquo;</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt; text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">--</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">项目负责人：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">虞之超</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A32%3A09%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%876.png?Expires=1971160329&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=dKCkFTpxNtgA8joSeDYX2csDgSI%3D" width="715" height="409" /></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 73.5pt;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（项目组：《红色大数据抖音创业》）</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt;">&laquo;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&ldquo;通过做这个项目，我得到了许多的锻炼与成长，对于我们本土的红色文化也有了一定的了解，现在我也在逐步发展自己的公司，未来我有信心能够用自己的力量去帮助更多需要帮助的人。&rdquo;</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt; text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">--</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">项目负责人：</span><strong style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">李鑫</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="15" style="text-indent: 0pt; margin-left: 42pt; text-align: right;" align="right">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A37%3A25%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%877.png?Expires=1971160645&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=SBCXQ%2FGjeg8SFJ2x0WRu5mjg7EE%3D" width="703" height="401" /></span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 项目组《传统陶瓷的链变之旅》</span></span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt;">&laquo;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&ldquo;通过参加创新创业大赛，我看到了更好的自己，也明白了一个团队的重要性。但还是希望老师在平常上创业创新课时，可以多教我们一些项目计划书、ppt的制作或者多和我们分析一些优秀的案例，让我们更好地去构建自己的创意王国。&rdquo;</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt; text-align: right;"><span style="text-align: right; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="text-align: right; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">--</span><span style="text-align: right; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">项目负责人：</span><strong style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">郑乐馨</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt; text-align: right;"><strong style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A40%3A08%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%878.png?Expires=1971160808&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=3AYizSNmcBxeOcWbFWnDoanslbU%3D" width="703" height="401" /></span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt; text-align: right;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（项目组：《</span>&ldquo;火眼金睛&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;分布式光伏发电无人机自动巡检系统》）</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt;">&laquo;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&ldquo;我们的项目理念是&ldquo;将学习与科研结合，用成果服务社会&rdquo;，团队对于一个项目的制作来说是十分重要的。参加这样一个比赛， 不仅增强了我们对于项目的了解，成员们都来自不同的专业，多个学科交叉融合，更是实现了1+1＞2的效果，同时也增强了我自身的领导力与团队的凝聚力。&rdquo;</span></p>
<p class="15" style="margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -21pt; text-align: right;"><span style="text-align: right; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="text-align: right; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;">--</span><span style="text-align: right; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">项目负责人：</span><strong style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">闻鹏</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在比赛的最后，聂永昭</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">评委</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">对于本次大赛项目进行了点评并给出了建议。他表示创业创新项目</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一是要更加突出专创。</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">专业与项目要融合，能体现出学校特色，用专业手段解决社会问题；</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">二是要更加注重应用场景和商业模式与价值。</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">项目如何盈利是一个值得深思的问题；</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">三是要更加关注职业和岗位的创新。</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">用创意开辟新的天地；</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">四是红旅项目要抓住大赛主旋律。</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在项目中要体现出可推广性以及不可复制性并直接或间接的展现带动就业数量。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/innovate/2022-06-21%2016%3A41%3A36%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%879.png?Expires=1971160896&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=9s4rbDxRDTWcf378%2BFF32Z1RakI%3D" width="708" height="404" /></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt; text-align: right;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（图：集体合照）</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">创业的细节在于创新，从一个想法的生根发芽到一个项目的落地实现，这其中所经历的、所成长的、所收获的，都将成为我们人生中最大的财富。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">此次大赛的成功举办为大学生搭建了</span>&ldquo;学院引导、教师指导、学生参与&rdquo;的创新创业展示平台，点燃激发了广大学生的创业热情，提高了大学生创新创业能力。同时，学校也将以此为契机，积极探索职业本科创新创业教育新模式，努力将创新创业教育贯穿人才培养全过程，以赛促学、以赛促教、以赛促创，培养更多高素质技术技人。</span></p>
<p class="15" style="text-indent: 0pt; margin-left: 42pt; text-align: right;" align="right">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="15" style="text-indent: 0pt; margin-left: 42pt; text-align: right;" align="right">&nbsp;</p>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (489, '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 高考已经过去两个月，经历了考试、查分、填报志愿、等待录取查询等事宜，小伙伴们总算画上了一个圆满的句号。就要开学了，作为一名准大学生,激动和兴奋的心都是应该有的。但是，如何办好相关手续，顺利入学，成为一名合格的大学生。今天，把新生入学的一些相关事宜分享给各位2022级的大学新生。</p>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、根据学校开学时间，尽早买票。省外的同学买票一定是头等大事的，收到录取通知书后就以考虑买票的事了。此外馨提示，你认为没有学生证就需要买全票，其实不是的，拿录取通知书作为凭证，同样可以买票打折。买入学的票，要是确定家人陪同一起入学，那就顺便把家人的返程票也买好。</p>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、依据录取通知书上的要求，办好相关手续新生入学须知，上面比如激活校园卡、注册办理电话卡等。如果你在校期间申请贫困补助，需要提前办好&ldquo;三级贫困&rdquo;证明。</p>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、关于新生入学考试这个事，你必须问清楚，可以到论坛贴吧去问问学姐学长。新生入学需要注意的事项很多，今天给大家说最为重要的事项,希望各位新生引起重视。最后，预祝各位小伙伴顺利入学、大学生活愉快！</p>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (490, '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: #333333; font-family: Gotham-Book, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Ubuntu, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei UI', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Source Han Sans CN', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">1、学生本人提出书面申请，出具乡、镇、街道盖章的《贫困生家庭经济情况调查表》，并填写《贫困生消费情况调查表》；</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: #333333; font-family: Gotham-Book, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Ubuntu, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei UI', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Source Han Sans CN', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">2、班级成立贫困生考核小组，成员5到7人，视班级人数多少而定，由本班里的党员、预备党员、入党积极分子、班干部及多数同学认可的普通同学代表组成，考核小组必须做到看问题客观，办事公平、公正，忌感情用事；</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: #333333; font-family: Gotham-Book, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Ubuntu, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei UI', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Source Han Sans CN', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">3、贫困生考核小组对申请贫困生的学生进行调查，其在校期间的生活表现，平时消费情况，充分征求同寝室同学的意见，必要时可通过查询消费情况予以确认；</p>
<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: #333333; font-family: Gotham-Book, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Ubuntu, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei UI', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Source Han Sans CN', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;">4、调查结果交给班主任，由班主任根据所掌握的情况综合衡量，进行初审后报学院审核。</p>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (491, '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">9月8日，为期三天的井冈山先锋数字创新创业培训班圆满结束，先锋软件集团董事长陈苏出席结业汇报会。江西软件大学井冈山数字经济产业学院20余名学生代表及入驻井冈山数字创新创业孵化基地的企业负责人参加汇报会。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">会上，陈苏董事长给与会者描绘了先锋软件集团井冈山数字经济产业园未来的发展图景。他鼓励学员们积极投身于数字创新创业实践活动，学以致用，努力探索适合自己的创新创业之路。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2022-09-08%2009%3A15%3A04%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=1977959704&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=00U%2BNYZhy4Ro%2BvJcM7V1FAKeGjU%3D" width="650" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2022-09-08%2009%3A15%3A22%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=1977959722&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=2eLx%2BTMsoRLqUR6hkfoUSCMmSks%3D" width="650" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">本次培训通过理论教学、案例分析、研讨交流相结合，融合体验式、项目参与式的方式开展，围绕数字化技术、数字化应用和数字化管理逐步讲解，逐层剖析，向学员们重点讲授数字创业准备和运营，深度了解数字创业动态，分析数字创业需求，掌握数字运营方案设计及实施，帮助入驻井冈山数字创新创业孵化基地的企业负责人熟悉并掌握数字创新创业思维与方法，了解数字商业模式在生产、销售、服务等方面的运用技巧，切实提高了参训学员的数字化理论知识素养和数字化创新创业能力。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2022-09-08%2009%3A15%3A49%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=1977959749&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=wpFVh2lQgT0QV7JlpDFTyUZrqLE%3D" width="650" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">结业汇报会上，每位学员分享了自己的创业想法，交流了学习体会。参训学员纷纷表示，本次培训具有很强的针对性和指导性，通过三天的学习交流拓宽了思路视野、增长了知识储备、学到了先进经验。培训后，争取通过自身努力争做数字创新创业的宣传员和奋进者，让青春在党和人民最需要的地方绽放绚丽之花。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2022-09-08%2009%3A16%3A22%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.png?Expires=1977959782&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=S7j2%2FK9lTHC%2BBPbzMUhOhbtkFPo%3D" width="650" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;" src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2022-09-08%2009%3A16%3A33%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.png?Expires=1977959793&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=EWi3CVS%2BjXwIoN6spEQ91z9%2FGNk%3D" width="650" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">下一步，学校将契合国家数字经济发展重大战略，建设井冈山先锋数字创新创业孵化基地，推动数字创新创业，形成规模化数字创客集群及大型数字创新创业生态圈。数字创新创业孵化基地将有效聚集数字创新资源及数字创新人才，积极整合社会资源，为大学生创新创业人才提供更多成长空间和实践机会，充分发挥好大学生青年在数字经济发展中的积极作用，为老区振兴和高质量发展贡献青春力量。</span></p>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (500, '<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; margin-bottom: 22.6pt; text-indent: 28pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">大学生是大众创业万众创新的生力军，支持大学生创新创业具有重要意义。为有效解决大学生创新创业实践中的关键问题，进一步提升大学生创新创业能力，优化就业</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">服务</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业学院</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">就高校毕业生创业相关政策进行梳理解读</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<h2><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">（一）</span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">办公场地无偿使用</span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对于批准入驻到</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;先锋创客小镇众创空间&rdquo;的创业项目免费提供办公场所，&ldquo;先锋创客小镇众创空间&rdquo;</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">配备桌椅、水、电、空调</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">、网络</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">等基础设施，创业者们可</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;拎包入驻&rdquo;</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法：</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">需申请办公场地的同学至</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业学院（创客大厦负一楼</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">-105办公室</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">）咨询办理，联系电话黄老师</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">13767979712</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<h2><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">（二）免费代理注册公司</span></strong></h2>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对于大学生自主创业，将免费为大学生办理个体工商户、企业工商注册登记手续，免收管理类、登记类和证照类等有关行政事业性收费。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法：</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">需代理注册企业的同学请至</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业学院（创客大厦负一楼</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">-105办公室</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">）咨询办理，联系电话黄老师</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">13767979712</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt;"><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（三）免费提供创业服务</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对于批准入驻众创空间的创业项目免费提供办公场地，有创业意愿的大学生，可免费获得公共就业和人才服务机构提供的创业指导服务，包括政策咨询、信息服务、项目开发、风险评估、开业指导、融资服务、跟踪扶持等</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;一条龙&rdquo;创业服务。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法：</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">需代理注册企业的同学请至</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业学院（创客大厦负一楼</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">-105办公室</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">）咨询办理，联系电话黄老师</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">13767979712</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（四）一次性创业补贴</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">5000元</span></span></strong></p>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; page-break-after: avoid; mso-pagination: lines-together; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对在本省行政区域内首次创办企业或从事个体经营且正常经营</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">6个月以上的在校生和毕业5年内的高校毕业生，可申请一次性创业补贴，补贴标准为5000元。</span></span></h2>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; page-break-after: avoid; mso-pagination: lines-together; line-height: 150%;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">：</span></span></h2>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 29.6pt; break-after: avoid; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">1）进入江西人社网上办事大厅（http://zwfw.rst.jiangxi.gov.cn:8081），点击&ldquo;个人办事&rdquo;&rarr;&ldquo;就业创业&rdquo;&rarr;&ldquo;一次性创业补贴申请&rdquo;；</span></span></h2>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; page-break-after: avoid; mso-pagination: lines-together; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">2）携带申报材料至创业地就业创业服务中心申领。</span></span></h2>
<h2><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（五）税收优惠</span></span></strong></h2>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">持人社部门核发《就业创业证》（注明</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;毕业年度内自主创业税收政策&rdquo;）的高校毕业生在毕业年度内（指毕业所在自然年，即1月1日至12月31日）创办个体工商户、个人独资企业的，3年内按每户每年8000元为限额依次扣减其当年实际应缴纳的营业税、城市维护建设税、教育费附加和个人所得税。对高校毕业生创办的小型微利企业，按国家规定享受相关税收支持政策。</span></span></p>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; page-break-after: avoid; mso-pagination: lines-together; line-height: 150%;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">：企业注册地所在的省财政厅、省税务局</span></span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt;"><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（六）创业担保贷款</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对具有大专以上学历（毕业年度在校学生视同毕业生）、</span> <span style="font-family: 仿宋;">初级以上专业技术职称、三级以上职业资格或职业等级的个</span> <span style="font-family: 仿宋;">人、高校毕业生（含大学生村官、留学回国学生、技工院校</span> <span style="font-family: 仿宋;">高级工班和预备技师班、特殊教育院校职业教育类毕业生）</span> <span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业的，可申请最高</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">30万元创业担保贷款；高校毕业生合 伙创业或组织起来共同创业的，根据符合条件的合伙（组织） 创业人数适当提高贷款额度，按合计最高额再提高不超过 10%确定，可申请最高200万元创业担保贷款；高校毕业生创办小微企业的，可申请最高600万元创业担保贷款。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">：</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">手机微信搜索</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;江西省创业担保贷款&rdquo;公众号，进入页面后点击&ldquo;贷款申请&rdquo;，按提示操作；</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">下载</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;江西农商银行e百福&rdquo;手机App，进入页面后点击&ldquo;创业贷&rdquo;，按提示操作；</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">3）支付宝搜索&ldquo;赣服通&rdquo;进入页面后点击&ldquo;创业担保贷款&rdquo;，按提示操作；</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">4）携带申报材料至创业地就业创业服务中心申请。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（七）申领《就业创业证》</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">高校毕业生可免费申领《就业创业登记证》，办理就业登记或失业登记，以便人社部门掌握就业状态，并凭证享受人社部门相应扶持政策。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">：</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">手机端：</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">1.进入&ldquo;支付宝&rdquo;APP，点击&ldquo;赣服通&rdquo;，找到&ldquo;人社服务&rdquo;的&ldquo;就业创业&rdquo;栏目，选择&ldquo;就业创业证申领&rdquo;。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">2.进入&ldquo;江西人社&rdquo;微信公众号，选择&ldquo;微服务&rdquo;，点击&ldquo;我要办事&rdquo;，进入&ldquo;就业创业&rdquo;栏目的&ldquo;就业失业登记&rdquo;，选择&ldquo;《就业创业证》申领&rdquo;。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">电脑端：进入江西人社网上办事大厅（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">http://zwfw.rst.jiangxi.gov.cn:8081），点击&ldquo;个人办事&rdquo;&rarr;&ldquo;就业创业&rdquo;&rarr;&ldquo;就业创业证申领&rdquo;。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">现场申请：携带身份证到户籍所在地或常住地或就业地的就业创业服务中心申领。咨询电话：</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">0791-83805598</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 11pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 11pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 仿宋;">江西软件职业技术大学</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新创业学院</span></span></p>
<h1><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Calibri Light'; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; font-size: 9.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 22.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong></h1>
<h1><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; font-size: 9.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 22.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong></h1>
<h1><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; font-size: 9.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 22.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong></h1>
<h1><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; font-size: 9.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 22.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong></h1>
<h1><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal; font-size: 9.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 22.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong></h1>');
INSERT INTO content VALUES (502, '<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; margin-bottom: 22.6pt; text-indent: 28pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">大学生是大众创业万众创新的生力军，支持大学生创新创业具有重要意义。为有效解决大学生创新创业实践中的关键问题，进一步提升大学生创新创业能力，优化就业</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">服务</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业学院</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">就高校毕业生创业相关政策进行梳理解读</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<h2><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">（一）</span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">办公场地无偿使用</span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对于批准入驻到</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;先锋创客小镇众创空间&rdquo;的创业项目免费提供办公场所，&ldquo;先锋创客小镇众创空间&rdquo;</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">配备桌椅、水、电、空调</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">、网络</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">等基础设施，创业者们可</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;拎包入驻&rdquo;</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法：</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">需申请办公场地的同学至</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业学院（创客大厦负一楼</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">-105办公室</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">）咨询办理，联系电话黄老师</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">13767979712</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<h2><strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 14.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">（二）免费代理注册公司</span></strong></h2>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对于大学生自主创业，将免费为大学生办理个体工商户、企业工商注册登记手续，免收管理类、登记类和证照类等有关行政事业性收费。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法：</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">需代理注册企业的同学请至</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业学院（创客大厦负一楼</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">-105办公室</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">）咨询办理，联系电话黄老师</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">13767979712</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt;"><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（三）免费提供创业服务</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对于批准入驻众创空间的创业项目免费提供办公场地，有创业意愿的大学生，可免费获得公共就业和人才服务机构提供的创业指导服务，包括政策咨询、信息服务、项目开发、风险评估、开业指导、融资服务、跟踪扶持等</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;一条龙&rdquo;创业服务。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法：</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">需代理注册企业的同学请至</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业学院（创客大厦负一楼</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">-105办公室</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">）咨询办理，联系电话黄老师</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">13767979712</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（四）一次性创业补贴</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">5000元</span></span></strong></p>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; page-break-after: avoid; mso-pagination: lines-together; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对在本省行政区域内首次创办企业或从事个体经营且正常经营</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">6个月以上的在校生和毕业5年内的高校毕业生，可申请一次性创业补贴，补贴标准为5000元。</span></span></h2>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; page-break-after: avoid; mso-pagination: lines-together; line-height: 150%;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">：</span></span></h2>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 29.6pt; break-after: avoid; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">1）进入江西人社网上办事大厅（http://zwfw.rst.jiangxi.gov.cn:8081），点击&ldquo;个人办事&rdquo;&rarr;&ldquo;就业创业&rdquo;&rarr;&ldquo;一次性创业补贴申请&rdquo;；</span></span></h2>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; page-break-after: avoid; mso-pagination: lines-together; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">2）携带申报材料至创业地就业创业服务中心申领。</span></span></h2>
<h2><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（五）税收优惠</span></span></strong></h2>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">持人社部门核发《就业创业证》（注明</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;毕业年度内自主创业税收政策&rdquo;）的高校毕业生在毕业年度内（指毕业所在自然年，即1月1日至12月31日）创办个体工商户、个人独资企业的，3年内按每户每年8000元为限额依次扣减其当年实际应缴纳的营业税、城市维护建设税、教育费附加和个人所得税。对高校毕业生创办的小型微利企业，按国家规定享受相关税收支持政策。</span></span></p>
<h2 style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; page-break-after: avoid; mso-pagination: lines-together; line-height: 150%;"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; line-height: 150%; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">：企业注册地所在的省财政厅、省税务局</span></span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt;"><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（六）创业担保贷款</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">对具有大专以上学历（毕业年度在校学生视同毕业生）、</span> <span style="font-family: 仿宋;">初级以上专业技术职称、三级以上职业资格或职业等级的个</span> <span style="font-family: 仿宋;">人、高校毕业生（含大学生村官、留学回国学生、技工院校</span> <span style="font-family: 仿宋;">高级工班和预备技师班、特殊教育院校职业教育类毕业生）</span> <span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创业的，可申请最高</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">30万元创业担保贷款；高校毕业生合 伙创业或组织起来共同创业的，根据符合条件的合伙（组织） 创业人数适当提高贷款额度，按合计最高额再提高不超过 10%确定，可申请最高200万元创业担保贷款；高校毕业生创办小微企业的，可申请最高600万元创业担保贷款。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">：</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">手机微信搜索</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;江西省创业担保贷款&rdquo;公众号，进入页面后点击&ldquo;贷款申请&rdquo;，按提示操作；</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">下载</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">&ldquo;江西农商银行e百福&rdquo;手机App，进入页面后点击&ldquo;创业贷&rdquo;，按提示操作；</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">3）支付宝搜索&ldquo;赣服通&rdquo;进入页面后点击&ldquo;创业担保贷款&rdquo;，按提示操作；</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">4）携带申报材料至创业地就业创业服务中心申请。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><strong><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">（七）申领《就业创业证》</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">高校毕业生可免费申领《就业创业登记证》，办理就业登记或失业登记，以便人社部门掌握就业状态，并凭证享受人社部门相应扶持政策。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 28.1000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 12.0000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #404040; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">申领办法</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">：</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">手机端：</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">1.进入&ldquo;支付宝&rdquo;APP，点击&ldquo;赣服通&rdquo;，找到&ldquo;人社服务&rdquo;的&ldquo;就业创业&rdquo;栏目，选择&ldquo;就业创业证申领&rdquo;。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">2.进入&ldquo;江西人社&rdquo;微信公众号，选择&ldquo;微服务&rdquo;，点击&ldquo;我要办事&rdquo;，进入&ldquo;就业创业&rdquo;栏目的&ldquo;就业失业登记&rdquo;，选择&ldquo;《就业创业证》申领&rdquo;。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">电脑端：进入江西人社网上办事大厅（</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">http://zwfw.rst.jiangxi.gov.cn:8081），点击&ldquo;个人办事&rdquo;&rarr;&ldquo;就业创业&rdquo;&rarr;&ldquo;就业创业证申领&rdquo;。</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">现场申请：携带身份证到户籍所在地或常住地或就业地的就业创业服务中心申领。咨询电话：</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">0791-83805598</span></span></p>
<p class="p" style="text-indent: 29.6000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.4000pt; margin: 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 11.3000pt 0.0000pt;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 11pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 11pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;">&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 仿宋;">江西软件职业技术大学</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right;" align="right"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; color: #3f3f3f; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 14pt; background: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">创新创业学院</span></span></p>
